{"tid":1718243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅-六月飛霜","createTime":"2019-11-13T20:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T21:55:13.000Z","uid":250869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40fe3b4b0aa7d3493810c2c0da0f45c04d099caf","tid":1718243,"uid":250869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:28:08.000Z","msg":"我正式宣佈這是反映2019年香港社會現況的重要歌曲之一。<br />\n<br />\n聽到喊撚左出黎<br />\n<br />\n每句歌詞配合什麼社會狀況，靠大家腦補。<br />\n<br />\n「最終 習慣為著獵取一身盔甲竟不怕損傷<br />\n為了夢幻日子得到保障 用惡夢結賬」<br />\n<br />\n「埋下理想栽種幻想」<br />\n<br />\n「欲求未滿 剩下砒霜 當菜汁分享<br />\n猶如吞仙丹上月亮 誰有膽設想這世間下場」<br />\n<br />\n「即使你跟我比鬥已極平常」<br />\n<br />\n「習慣了這異象 誰又在叫嚷」<br />\n<br />\n「人人一把口一百種真相 誰說得漂亮」"},{"pid":"baef30d2164fc8d78566f8b8be2bb675a8e80a90","tid":1718243,"uid":250869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:28:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KlIoLizlF3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKlIoLizlF3s&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=2a35e8da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KlIoLizlF3s</a>"},{"pid":"024d3f2e5e61356e44d1d474e172e30b4c95c203","tid":1718243,"uid":201240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:29:10.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"3d7b5019da4f37ac4496c565bb8357914bdc6733","tid":1718243,"uid":44297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:34:07.000Z","msg":"真相！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vhWwJUDlOaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvhWwJUDlOaI&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=8b957c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vhWwJUDlOaI</a>"},{"pid":"9512bf8bca1b4cb4cb7eba2b107d763cd6586ca1","tid":1718243,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T20:45:55.000Z","msg":"藍奕邦 識唔識<br />\n單春陳收皮啦"},{"pid":"a8436b253cda409d52deacdf7b5774d8a73e8162","tid":1718243,"